{"tid":1718916,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[DIY] 復活蛋製作","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:34:50.000Z","uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbe2576f54ad4a5d3e2b63434faebd7dc9a6717","tid":1718916,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"唔知大家細個有冇整過復活蛋, 我諗起細細個幼稚園都會教整復活蛋。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;一般人做復活蛋時，為了方便多是將蛋煮熟或取生雞蛋直接上色，但這樣的存放方式較短，<br />\n其實不妨在雞蛋較渾圓的一端穿一個小洞(用小匙打幾下再小心拎開碎殼就可以)，把蛋液取出可下廚再利用，也不用擔心雞蛋變質，而且蛋殼本身也可以靠這個小洞站立。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我就發現左整完個蛋殼洗乾淨之後可以加果汁, 用膠紙/blutack小心封口再雪凍, <br />\n打爛個蛋殼就會有蛋形既果汁冰食喇, 小朋友好中意。<br />\n<br />\n咁蛋殼入面仲可以加Ｄ咩液體去制作, 就由大家發揮創意喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f635704a6b39359e04ced3c0271e47e389d537c8","tid":1718916,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"自推(1/10)"},{"pid":"2513621252898ebd895a7f1795a05fef7273b820","tid":1718916,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"自推(2/10)"},{"pid":"bcd74fdd2a39f9b2092339d3571529efb3fd2a8c","tid":1718916,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:25:14.000Z","msg":"自推(3/10)"},{"pid":"5ccb52c38a773d006a382428ad9b14d242a29f8f","tid":1718916,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c2f36c9a426f73e176a48cb297c75c5904bba4","tid":1718916,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"自推(4/10)"},{"pid":"5837d3903369dcb5c2724cd73d5cea472fe23b80","tid":1718916,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"自推(5/10)"},{"pid":"59a841c1d0c25d15f8ed71df1e5154973372d5b2","tid":1718916,"uid":130203